            <p><add hand="#barker">Order for medicine.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><persName>Mr Moses Austin</persName></p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>You'l be as kind as to [send] me, one viol of that
Medicine which was in the same; I have be taken with the Rumitis
in one of my 'Leggs' that I am not able to walk a bout</p>

<p>[Peter Love.]</p>
<p><placeName>Mine A Burton</placeName> <date when="1811-03-20">20th March 1811</date></p>

        </div1>
